Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的問題 還是直接去找本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏沉睡著他的遺傳基因
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且祭品還活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不像感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是午飯的關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 昨天就有些不對勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修煉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍術修煉 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們啊 鳴人的身體不適…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好認真教我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的英雄不過如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 你們聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要戰勝各種困難和挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是體力和運動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但漫無目的地鍛煉無益於實戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…經過我的長年修煉 研究出一套方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為 鳴人流強勁動力以及神奇訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來很帶勁 哥哥也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握了它 危難時刻你們也能大展身手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡太辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼事 都需要百分百的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先飛奔到河邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說佯攻是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是連這都不懂的笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 我是說被兜利用真是太丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以不死之身為榮的你竟會被分屍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠可憐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不是一樣 自爆身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是為了終極藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最崇高的自我獻身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少狡辯 還不是掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 訓練…結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一身汗 真輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買些飲料來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 真不像樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…身體不太舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是英雄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你總是嚷著藝術 藝術的 煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡做些造型醜陋的炸彈 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那狗屁儀式才是又臭又長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得我還得挺身掩護你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不需要你掩護呢 冒牌的藝術家混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少叫囂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了那咒印 你一文不值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就嘗嘗我的詛咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計你會先被我的藝術給炸飛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱身運動已經做過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃那邊的冰激淋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧看吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 很好吃吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再見一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直都在你們身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然完全沒減肥的概念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我傷勢痊癒 一定會運動的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我嚴厲地指導你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掠奪 掠奪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:12:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去…快出去… 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以對哥哥說這麼過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被討厭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做錯什麼了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真沒事嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…小櫻…不用啦…那裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼擔心你 跟傻瓜似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…鎮長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之為了儘快通知各位 就匆忙趕來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:14:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早 這名老者徘徊於鎮政廳之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆都平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村長能平安歸來才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛被刺傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我彷徨於荒野之時 總算得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多克 真是給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件重要的事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得那晚我給你的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你已經察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是藏於村子祭壇裏寶物的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為防被偷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將其拆散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給了你及另一名守衛保管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜的是 我和他保管的五根都被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅剩的兩根 無論如何都要保住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把它交給迪索納斯嚴加保管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…剩下的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 你好奇怪 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穢土轉生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真機靈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來很特別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被騙了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住那個胖子 拷問出情報來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半死不活的祭品看來派不上多大用場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:17:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掠奪 掠奪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:19:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去 快出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:18:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去 快出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快從鳴人哥哥的體內出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,像你這樣擁有強大力量的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.11,0:22:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,無論將之用於正道或是邪道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:22:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,都必須背負巨大的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,但是你的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,為何想要變強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,力量 第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.79,0:23:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,這份執念一定會指引你前進的
